00:16:28,640 --> 00:16:33,700
Both times I didn't open. Donna Kira came up with a train near noon. She didn't knock.

191
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:39,000
She left the tray on the floor against the door with a note under the plate. I waited for

192
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:43,860
her footsteps to fade and opened the door the smallest crack. I pulled the tray inside.

