202
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:49,260
24 hours that my face made a movement. It wasn't pain. I know. I answered. I hung up. Lay down again.

203
00:17:49,660 --> 00:17:54,280
And this time I managed to cry without being angry at myself for crying. I spent all of Friday

204
00:17:54,280 --> 00:17:59,700
outside that door. Not the whole time. There was a chair in the corridor, a moss-coloured velvet armchair

