00:18:09,880 --> 00:18:14,320
questions and went down with short answers. Fausto asked to speak with me over the intercom.

208
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:19,380
I sent word that not today. I leaned my forehead against the door's wood near the end of the

209
00:18:19,380 --> 00:18:25,260
afternoon, and spoke low without calling her name. The wood was cold. I let it stay that way.

210
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:31,420
I wrote that before you existed in my life. I stopped. Before I knew you'd exist in my life,

211
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:36,880
I stopped again. That doesn't fix anything I know. On the other side her silence had wait.

212
00:18:37,280 --> 00:18:42,920
I could tell her silence is a part. There was her thoughtful silence, her wounded silence,

213
00:18:43,280 --> 00:18:48,740
her sleeping silence. That was a new silence, a silence that was weighing on me in return.

214
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:53,980
I didn't ask to come in. I didn't have the right. The clause I'd written with my own hand,

215
00:18:53,980 --> 00:18:59,100
in the week I decided to buy her from the Sarah Valls, was the only piece of my history with her

