00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:13,080
I'd be confirming the paragraph. I went back to the study at eight. I called Bastion.

219
00:19:13,580 --> 00:19:19,680
You know this house. I do. Find every copy of that contract. My mother's Fausto's the one I

