00:22:47,440 --> 00:22:53,140
learned to read in the coming days, and that something was respect. He was letting me choose the distance.

258
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:58,840
At the end of the afternoon I went up again. I passed the door of his study. The door was a jar.

