00:23:10,620 --> 00:23:15,040
As if the work had come back to fill every hour I was away. He was reading a sheet with an

262
00:23:15,040 --> 00:23:20,660
attention that hurt to look at. He raised his eyes and saw me. He didn't move. He didn't smile.

