264
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:32,620
Good night. I said, good night. That was all. I continued down the corridor. I went to the

265
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:37,840
suite that was hours and didn't go in. I went to the old contract room. I laid dressed on the

266
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:44,220
