297
00:26:44,540 --> 00:26:50,500
Ludovico had left a standing order at some ordinary cafe. Months ago. Without telling me. Without

298
00:26:50,500 --> 00:26:55,800
asking for anything in return. Without collecting. Like a man leaving a piece of home on every

