301
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:13,860
taste came along with a new scar. I paid. Left. Fausto Ranieri's office was on the second floor

302
00:27:13,860 --> 00:27:20,360
of a dark brick building. Three blocks ahead. Bastion parked. Stayed in the car. I went up the stairs

