00:27:27,040 --> 00:27:32,160
The secretary tried to stop me. I walked straight past. With the politeness of someone who no

305
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:37,720
longer asks permission. Fausto was behind the desk. Glasses at the tip of his nose. A paper

