00:30:47,220 --> 00:30:52,220
She just ran her hand over my back. The way her grandmother must have run her hand over her as a

338
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:57,600
child. Then she got up, went to the kitchen, came back with a mug of bad coffee and a piece of

