00:31:11,660 --> 00:31:16,360
The draft in Faustos drawer. I told all of it in the messy way you tell your best friend,

342
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:22,660
out of order, with repetition, with a pause to breathe. I told her about the belly. Narina stopped

343
00:31:23,160 --> 00:31:28,280
the piece of cake fell into her lap. She looked at me as if seeing me for the first time in three

344
00:31:28,280 --> 00:31:36,280
days. I, Alanda, I know she cried. Then laughed. Then cried again. Hugged me tight enough to hurt my

345
00:31:36,280 --> 00:31:43,140
shoulder. You're not fighting just for yourself, girl. She said, still on my shoulder. This changes the game.

346
00:31:43,600 --> 00:31:49,460
I  breathed  deep  inside  her  hug.  It  really  does  change  it.  She  let  me  go.  Wipe  her  face  on

