00:32:13,820 --> 00:32:20,500
Nurt. To the doctor, Alanda. Not tomorrow. Today. You look like you haven't slept in three days.

353
00:32:20,500 --> 00:32:24,900
And there's a little one in there who needs a mother who's whole. There was no arguing.

354
00:32:25,480 --> 00:32:29,760
Nareena put shoes on me. Put a person in my hand. Pushed me out of the apartment.

355
00:32:30,460 --> 00:32:35,280
Bastion lifted his head from the seat when he saw me. Looked at Nareena in the doorway. She came

